### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Analytical query — ClickHouse-backed historical candle queries
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### This file validates the analytical query surface added in S149.
### These endpoints query ClickHouse directly (not NATS KV) for historical data.
###
### Prerequisites:
###   make up           # starts full stack including clickhouse + writer
###   make seed-multi   # seeds configctl with btcusdt + ethusdt bindings
###   wait ~120s        # writer needs to flush batches to ClickHouse
###
### Note: These endpoints return 503 if ClickHouse is not configured in gateway.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### --- Analytical candle history ---

### 1. Basic analytical candle query — btcusdt 60s (default limit=50)
### Expected: 200 with candles array + source="clickhouse"
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Analytical candle query with limit — btcusdt 60s (last 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Analytical candle query with time range
### since/until are unix seconds. Adjust to current time window.
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&since=1710000000&until=1710003600&limit=100
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Analytical candle query — ethusdt 300s
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=300&limit=20
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Analytical candle query — large limit (up to 500)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&limit=500
Accept: application/json

###

### --- Error handling ---

### 6. Missing timeframe — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Invalid limit (> 500) — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&limit=9999
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. since after until — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytical/evidence/candles?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&since=1710003600&until=1710000000
Accept: application/json

###

